locations.title: Il Duomo's Secret
locations.description:
Seal of Iltani - Poison

Altair's Amor is the most powerful armor in the game and is locked away underneath Villa Monteriggioni. In Sequence 4, you'll visit "Novella's Secret" with Mario and unlock the Assassin Tomb side missions across Italy. In each Assassin Tomb, you'll find the tomb of a famous assassin and a round seal. To unlock Altair's Amor, find all six seals and place them into their slots in the crypt under Monteriggioni.
